页面完整但细节普通，按钮、卡片、图表、图标和间距仍像快速拼装。\n4-6: 多数组件完成度较好，间距和局部样式稳定，但精修程度和资产质量仍有限。\n6-8: 局部细节高度统一，组件、图标、图表、插图和状态都像完整产品设计系统的一部分。", "weight": 0.15, "weight_percent": 15}, {"desc": "评估静态截图中的基础可读、可辨认和可操作性。它不是产品功能评分，只用于防止明显不可读、遮挡、错位、核心结构失败的页面被视觉氛围抬高。", "display_id": "A6", "hard_fail": false, "id": "basic_usability", "name": "基础可用性", "score_rule": "0-2: 核心信息不可读，按钮/输入/导航被遮挡或错位，布局严重影响理解。\n2-4: 基本能理解，但存在明显拥挤、溢出、低对比、遮挡或响应式问题。\n4-6: 主要内容和操作清楚，只有局部小问题，不明显阻碍静态理解。\n6-8: 信息清晰、控件可辨认、结构稳定，桌面/移动截图中都没有明显基础可用性问题。", "weight": 0.05, "weight_percent": 5}], "aggregate_formula": "single_canonical_screenshot_score", "aggregate_view": "image", "available_viewports": ["image"], "backend": "command", "errors": [], "extra_info_scores": {"aesthetics": {"adaptive_viewports": "off", "aggregate_strategy": "single_canonical_screenshot_score", "aggregate_view": "image", "axis_scores": {"basic_usability": 0.6, "color_material": 0.6, "composition_hierarchy": 0.4, "detail_finish": 0.0, "typography": 0.1, "visual_impact_originality": 0.7}, "designer_review": null, "occlusion_overlap_affected_axes": [], "occlusion_overlap_check": "always_on", "occlusion_overlap_detected": false, "occlusion_overlap_issue": {"affected_axes": [], "count": 0, "detected": false, "evidence": [], "highest_severity": "none", "status": "none", "targets": [], "types": []}, "occlusion_overlap_status": "none", "occlusion_overlap_types": [], "profile": "aesthetic_v4", "rubric_version": "aesthetic_static_v1", "score": 0.4, "score_100": 5.0, "score_scale": "0-8", "status": "success", "weighted_scores": {"basic_usability": 0.03, "color_material": 0.09, "composition_hierarchy": 0.08, "detail_finish": 0.0, "typography": 0.015, "visual_impact_originality": 0.21}, "weighted_total": 0.425}}, "final_score": 0.4, "id": "Case-01-low-power-001-card.dsl", "input_path": "D:\\code\\A2UI\\vlm\\aesthetic-v4-vlm-judge-package-20260624\\a2ui_png\\Case-01-low-power-001-card.dsl.png", "occlusion_findings": [], "occlusion_overlap_affected_axes": [], "occlusion_overla